--------------------------------------
Text Color Mod [2.5]
Written by Plexol since Version [1.0]
--------------------------------------
1.| Copy & Paste the file csgo_plexol.txt inside this folder:

		[A:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\common\Counter-Strike Global Offensive\csgo\resource]
		
2.| Add [-language plexol] in launch options without brackets.
3.| Restart your game.
________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

--------------------------------------
Radio Panels [2.0]
Written by Plexol since version [1.0]
--------------------------------------
1.| Open this folder:

		[B:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\common\Counter-Strike Global Offensive\csgo\resource\ui]
		
2.| Replace the radiopanel.txt file with the new file (it's recommended to take a backup first).
3.| Restart the game.
________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

--------------------------------
Custom CSGO Fonts
Created by Spddl
Website: http://fonts.spddl.de/
--------------------------------
1.| Unzip & place the (Steam) folder directly into your Program Files directory that has (Steam).

				[Usually "C:\Program Files\ or D:\Program Files (x86)]
				
2.| When it asks you to replace the (Steam) folder; click [Yes, Replace All].

																									[!!!WARNING!!!]
									Each download not coming from this site could have been modified using a virus or other unwanted modifications wich could result in a VAC ban.
________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

--------------------------------------
Autoexec Configuration [3.2]
Written by Plexol since Version [1.0]
--------------------------------------
1.| 1.| Copy & Paste the file (autoexec.cfg) inside this folder:

		[E:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\common\Counter-Strike Global Offensive\csgo\cfg]
		
2.| Add [-exec autoexec] in launch options without brackets.
3.| Restart your game.
_______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

--------------------------------------
Props & Entities Spawner [4.2]
Written by Plexol since Version [1.0]
--------------------------------------

1.| Copy the file/folder "autoexec.cfg" (file) & "Props_Entities" (folder); Paste into this folder:

		[F:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\common\Counter-Strike Global Offensive\csgo\cfg]
		
2.| Add [-exec autoexec] in launch options without brackets.
3.| Restart the game.
4.| Host a server and invite anyone or play alone.
5.| Type [sv_cheats 1] in the console.
6.| Type [alias] in console to see the commands available.
7.| Execute a command of your choice from the list by typing "CommandName" in the console

		[Example:] Spawn a banana, type in console: banana
		[Example:] Remove all spawned Props & Entities, type in console: removeall
_______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

---------------
Video Settings
---------------

1.| Copy & Paste both (video.txt) and (videodefaults.txt) into the directory below.

		C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\userdata\224687114\[Steam ID]\local\cfg
		
2.| Run CSGO and check the Video Settings and compare with the photo provided.
3.| If settings are not the same; change them to be identical.
_______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________	

---------------
Launch Options
---------------

1.| Start Steam & Go to Library.
2.| Find CSGO and [right-click] the game.
3.| Click [properties].
4.| Make sure you're on the (General) tab & click [Set Launch Options...]
5.| Copy & Paste the below launch options & click [Ok].
		
																									[Launch Settings]
							-exec autoexec -language plexol -noforcemaccel -noforcemparms -noforcemspd -noforcemspeed -novid -nosync -nojoy -high -port 27041 -tickrate 128 -cl_disablehtmlmotd 1
